Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.48,0:00:05.73,Caption Top,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5\fs20}To Mr. Junichi Katsuragi
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.48,0:00:05.73,Caption Top,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5\fs20}I empathize with you. You were right about the way things are, \Nbut we should stand up for ourselves. And so, I have decided to form\N a publishing company together with a few of our comrades joining\N forces. I would like you to see it as the same battle but in a new \Nform, and hope you will join me in this endeavor. I want to talk to \Nyou about this face to face.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.48,0:00:05.73,Caption Top,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5\fs20}- Arita
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.49,0:00:11.00,Caption Top,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}- Arita
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.21,0:00:15.51,Songs,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.51,0:00:21.00,Songs,,0000,0000,0000,,I forget what I was like before I met you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.36,0:00:25.41,Songs,,0000,0000,0000,,The wind caresses my cheek
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.41,0:00:27.74,Songs,,0000,0000,0000,,♪Lullaby of Birdland♪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.74,0:00:32.31,Songs,,0000,0000,0000,,Kick my heels going down the slope
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.22,0:00:35.73,Songs,,0000,0000,0000,,As my worthless shadow grows　
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.73,0:00:40.84,Songs,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like an endless summer vacation
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.84,0:00:46.54,Songs,,0000,0000,0000,,Feels like sneakin' into the swimming pool
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.54,0:00:52.60,Songs,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, let's swim with our clothes on, jump in!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.60,0:00:55.27,Songs,,0000,0000,0000,,A shocking seductive spiral
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.27,0:00:59.77,Songs,,0000,0000,0000,,This beat that pierces my heart is strange　
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.00,0:01:03.18,Songs,,0000,0000,0000,,(It flares up, then vanishes)　
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.18,0:01:05.37,Songs,,0000,0000,0000,,Every miserable day is swell,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.37,0:01:06.31,Songs,,0000,0000,0000,,dress it up
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.31,0:01:09.90,Songs,,0000,0000,0000,,A high-speed swing surrounds us
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.96,0:01:13.88,Songs,,0000,0000,0000,,(What's this dance called? I can't stop)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.88,0:01:17.96,Songs,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you go, it's twined around my ears
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.96,0:01:23.14,Songs,,0000,0000,0000,,and won't leave me ever again
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.30,0:01:26.42,Songs,,0000,0000,0000,,This melody...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.82,0:01:31.90,Songs,,0000,0000,0000,,...is like love
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.20,0:01:44.94,Main Dialog,Tokie,0000,0000,0000,,A Christmas party?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.94,0:01:46.54,Main Dialog,Girl A,0000,0000,0000,,And we can go, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.54,0:01:48.76,Main Dialog,Maruo,0000,0000,0000,,Of course. It's next Sunday.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.76,0:01:50.33,Main Dialog,Girls A-B-C-D,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be there!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.33,0:01:53.26,Main Dialog,Tokie,0000,0000,0000,,Since it's an Olympus party, \Nwill you play guitar for us?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.04,0:01:56.51,Main Dialog,Maruo,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if you've got a request...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.68,0:02:00.75,Main Dialog,Tokie,0000,0000,0000,,Ri-chan, are you coming to \Nthe Christmas party, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.58,0:02:03.89,Main Dialog,Tokie,0000,0000,0000,,You can go with Nishimi-san, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.30,0:02:08.61,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not really part of \Nthat group, so I'll pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.61,0:02:14.45,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I can't make it. There's a \NChristmas party at the church on Sunday.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.83,0:02:17.22,Main Dialog,Maruo,0000,0000,0000,,Then Kawabuchi-kun is going to that, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.22,0:02:18.00,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.68,0:02:20.31,Main Dialog,Maruo,0000,0000,0000,,We should've checked before...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.78,0:02:25.20,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Maruo-kun. If you don't mind, I think \NI'd like to go to the party after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.74,0:02:26.71,Main Dialog,Maruo,0000,0000,0000,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.71,0:02:28.93,Main Dialog,Maruo,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, you're very welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.93,0:02:31.71,Main Dialog,Maruo,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}I never thought you'd agree \Nto come, Nishimi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.79,0:02:33.78,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Like this, little by little, it's \Nbest to put some distance between us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.83,0:02:34.70,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.64,0:02:40.76,Main Dialog,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.76,0:02:43.18,Main Dialog,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,You're late, Richie-baby!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.18,0:02:45.68,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hi...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.68,0:02:48.44,Main Dialog,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! Next we'll play the Spiders.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.44,0:02:49.73,Main Dialog,Yamaoka,0000,0000,0000,,What about the Beatles?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.73,0:02:52.19,Main Dialog,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go with "Bang Bang Bang"!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.93,0:03:03.10,Main Dialog,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Nishimi-san, how about some cider?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.37,0:03:04.27,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.69,0:03:10.12,Songs,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,Feigning innocence, bang bang bang!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.50,0:03:15.41,Songs,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,Bang bang, bababababababa-bang!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.60,0:03:20.60,Songs,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,He's someone I can't beat!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.67,0:03:25.10,Songs,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,Bang bang, bababababababa-bang!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.10,0:03:28.04,Main Dialog,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Nishimi-san, let's sing together!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.52,0:03:31.31,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really know the popular songs...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.03,0:03:39.89,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what {\i1}he's{\i0} doing right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.64,0:03:44.33,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe he's talking to Ri-chan at the church?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.73,0:04:12.00,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I go to a party and all I do \Nis think about those two...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.34,0:04:14.28,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like a fool...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.59,0:04:15.86,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Kaoru-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.98,0:04:18.15,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Ri-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.65,0:04:21.45,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you here? I thought \Nyou were going to church...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.25,0:04:26.63,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. The church's Christmas party is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.45,0:04:30.41,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,He isn't here with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.96,0:04:33.71,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Does he have to be?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.60,0:04:39.34,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Um... He went home with the little ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.27,0:04:41.31,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.24,0:04:44.34,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,It's cold, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.34,0:04:45.35,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.62,0:04:48.06,Main Dialog,Sailor,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.60,0:04:50.02,Main Dialog,Sailor,0000,0000,0000,,I got you, baby!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.98,0:05:08.71,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, it's \Nalmost his birthday, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.56,0:05:12.01,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I hope you finish in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.59,0:05:14.50,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Why...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.54,0:05:17.00,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you say things like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.13,0:05:19.34,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,You're wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.34,0:05:20.28,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,This is for...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.62,0:05:24.34,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind! Kaoru-san, you're an idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.51,0:05:31.68,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,What did I do this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.69,0:05:33.88,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.33,0:05:37.19,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,It's hard to understand women.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.45,0:05:42.82,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Why did I lose my temper like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.19,0:05:48.16,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one who rejected \NKaoru-san in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.26,0:05:54.15,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I finished knitting this, there's \Nno way I'd be able to give it to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.60,0:06:26.18,Main Dialog,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,I'm relieved.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.18,0:06:30.87,Main Dialog,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,You're safe for now Yurika, \Nbut let me tell you something...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.87,0:06:34.37,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,I know. You're going to tell \Nme not to see him, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.37,0:06:36.25,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to keep repeating yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.50,0:06:39.16,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Chet... no!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.08,0:06:41.18,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Chet!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.97,0:06:55.73,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Sentaro... What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.22,0:06:59.48,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,What am I...? I've been waitin' for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.48,0:07:03.26,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,W-Why are you acting so formal?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.48,0:07:08.55,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Ri'ko...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.13,0:07:12.10,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.21,0:07:17.61,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,I never realized how you felt 'til now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.61,0:07:22.62,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,I may have said dumb things an' hurt you...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.27,0:07:27.47,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. But... um... how can I put it...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.41,0:07:31.74,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,But about your feelings, I, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.94,0:07:43.73,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Sentaro, why are you suddenly \Non your best behavior?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.04,0:07:47.67,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it already. This isn't a yakuza movie.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.74,0:07:49.97,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Did I get it wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.74,0:07:56.33,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. You got it wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.82,0:08:03.02,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,O-Oh, a misunderstanding. \NSorry for talkin' so weird...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.02,0:08:07.68,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right! We're like family. You made \Nme nervous for a second there...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.89,0:08:12.12,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,I-In that case, good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.10,0:08:20.21,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,We're like family, so I couldn't stand \Nthe thought of causin' you pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.67,0:08:29.22,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad I heard this now, \Nand not a while back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.95,0:08:31.86,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,What's that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.41,0:08:36.46,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm never going to tell a blockhead like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.13,0:08:49.67,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,There's something I have to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.58,0:08:53.43,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going back to Tokyo soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.60,0:09:00.10,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,I probably won't see you again...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.41,0:09:08.08,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,An upperclassman from my college is \Nstarting up his own publishing company
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.08,0:09:10.07,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,and he wants me to help him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.97,0:09:13.53,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,I plan on leaving soon after New Year's.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.23,0:09:17.03,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,It's taken me a long time \Nto get to this point,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.03,0:09:20.46,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,but I owe it to you for making me think \NI should give going back one more try.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.46,0:09:21.60,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,I'm grateful.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.14,0:09:26.48,Main Dialog,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,"Idiot. I don't want to hear those words.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.48,0:09:28.59,Main Dialog,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,Just don't leave me..."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.00,0:09:32.34,Main Dialog,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't bring myself to say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.88,0:09:36.55,Main Dialog,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,Not when he's finally trying to move forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.10,0:09:42.56,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Ritsuko-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.80,0:09:45.16,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Yurika-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.16,0:09:47.26,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,W-What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.26,0:09:48.90,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Looking for something.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.90,0:09:52.24,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,I carelessly threw something \Naway that was important to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.91,0:09:55.15,Main Dialog,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, is that girl homeless?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.15,0:09:56.44,Main Dialog,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Ritsuko-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.94,0:09:59.50,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind me. Please, go on ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.50,0:10:03.81,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,A beautiful girl like you shouldn't be seen \Ndoing something like this, Yurika-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.84,0:10:06.88,Main Dialog,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,Ritsuko-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.90,0:10:11.98,Main Dialog,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,I'll help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.06,0:10:17.06,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,P-Please, don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.06,0:10:18.39,Main Dialog,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,It's something important, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.83,0:10:21.09,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Yurika-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.79,0:10:24.55,Main Dialog,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,So... what am I looking for?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.36,0:10:29.44,Main Dialog,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,Here it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.44,0:10:30.54,Main Dialog,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,This is it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.54,0:10:31.57,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.55,0:10:36.07,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,But I'll have to start \Nover with clean yarn...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.07,0:10:38.70,Main Dialog,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,Is this going to be a present for someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.45,0:10:40.63,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.87,0:10:44.25,Main Dialog,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you throw away \Nsomething so important?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.04,0:10:51.50,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,I was confused.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.19,0:10:58.33,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,I suddenly felt stupid for knitting a \Ngift that I'd never be able to give.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.60,0:11:00.38,Main Dialog,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,Why wouldn't you be able to?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.38,0:11:04.43,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,B-Because a lot of things \Nhave happened between us...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.43,0:11:07.36,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,...and I once hurt him terribly.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.36,0:11:08.60,Main Dialog,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,You turned him down, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.06,0:11:11.52,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,And I couldn't tell him I \Nlike him now, after all that,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.52,0:11:12.77,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,so I decided to let it go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.86,0:11:16.53,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,But then I thought that wouldn't do.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.33,0:11:22.40,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,See, there was another time when \NI said nothing and just gave up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.63,0:11:25.25,Main Dialog,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,Do you regret it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.25,0:11:29.93,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,No. I'd given up on that long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.72,0:11:33.94,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, I've realized \Nthis person has been there
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.94,0:11:37.69,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,to support me all this time, \Nwhenever I've felt down.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.49,0:11:43.43,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,I had no confidence in myself, but \Nhe did his best to encourage me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.19,0:11:46.77,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,This time, I want to be the \None to tell him how I feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.11,0:11:52.13,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,I finally decided to stop keeping my \Nmouth shut and waiting for things to end.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.42,0:11:59.61,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for talking about this...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.61,0:12:02.14,Main Dialog,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm glad you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.82,0:12:04.72,Main Dialog,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,I think you've opened my eyes as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.28,0:12:07.14,Main Dialog,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.49,0:12:09.39,Main Dialog,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.39,0:12:10.91,Main Dialog,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,Who's your prince, Ritsuko-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.91,0:12:12.86,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.45,0:12:15.06,Main Dialog,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,Shall I try and guess?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.06,0:12:18.22,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,W-W-What are you saying?! Please, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.85,0:12:20.32,Main Dialog,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,You're so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.44,0:12:34.74,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I'm set to leave this weekend.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.91,0:12:39.61,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Working in Tokyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.61,0:12:43.22,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. A lot happened at college \Nand I ended up dropping out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.62,0:12:48.82,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,But you'll come back once in a while, \Nwon't you? Like you've been doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.33,0:12:52.48,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,No. I'm never coming back to this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.33,0:12:57.53,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,Kaoru-kun, our sessions were fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.84,0:12:59.86,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,I'll miss seeing you and Sen-boy,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.86,0:13:02.19,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,but I don't want you guys \Nto stop playing jazz.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.70,0:13:06.83,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Brother Jun! Did you tell him \Nyou were going back to Tokyo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.36,0:13:14.60,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Sen!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.61,0:13:18.12,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,What's the hubbub, Richie?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.91,0:13:21.38,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,It's about Brother Jun!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.38,0:13:24.31,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, he's about to go back to Tokyo, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.31,0:13:25.82,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,I heard from Pops.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.00,0:13:29.32,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Well, ain't got nothin' to do with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.32,0:13:32.29,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wanna jam?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.29,0:13:34.44,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,You're gonna let that be \Nthe last you see of him?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.66,0:13:37.45,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothin' to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.29,0:13:42.01,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,You looked up to him as a big \Nbrother since you were a kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.49,0:13:46.52,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,You may never get the \Nchance to meet him again!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.52,0:13:48.10,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,There'd be no point.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.10,0:13:50.47,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Once he's gone, it'll be too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.68,0:13:54.16,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Enough about Brother Jun already.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.52,0:13:55.73,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get started here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.14,0:14:09.71,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't feel like \Npracticin', I'm goin' home.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.63,0:14:18.74,Main Dialog,Old Woman,0000,0000,0000,,What's all the fuss about?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.74,0:14:23.09,Main Dialog,Man,0000,0000,0000,,I guess college students from Tokyo \Nand all over have come to demonstrate
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.09,0:14:25.26,Main Dialog,Man,0000,0000,0000,,against letting the nuclear \Naircraft carrier into port.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.85,0:14:28.60,Main Dialog,Old Woman,0000,0000,0000,,That's terrible...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.56,0:14:32.47,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,In their eyes, I'm a traitor.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.41,0:14:36.48,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,They may never forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.43,0:14:38.49,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.94,0:14:44.99,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,...all I can do is search \Nin my own way from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.59,0:14:47.80,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,Using a different method than them...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.42,0:14:59.88,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're here, Richie.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.88,0:15:00.97,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Here, eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.35,0:15:03.94,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,I made it myself, so it \Nmight be a little salty...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.88,0:15:06.35,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,But if you're not gonna eat it, I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.82,0:15:08.93,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Is this any time to be eating?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.70,0:15:11.85,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Did you forget what I said last time?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.13,0:15:15.98,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talkin' about?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.22,0:15:19.43,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Don't play dumb! Are you going to \Nbe stubborn 'til it's too late?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.69,0:15:23.68,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Brother Jun is leaving this \Ntown today or tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.06,0:15:25.16,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,It's today.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.74,0:15:28.49,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,I'm taking the night train, Kaoru-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.58,0:15:35.24,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,Sen-boy, this was rather \Nold-fashioned of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.58,0:15:36.00,Caption Top,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Letter of Challenge
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.24,0:15:37.27,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it was some kind of joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.27,0:15:39.10,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,It's no joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.10,0:15:42.91,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to try havin' a serious \Nshowdown with you, Brother Jun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.95,0:15:48.05,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Wait... You're not really...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.07,0:15:50.30,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,I made it in time?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.30,0:15:51.74,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Let me in on it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.33,0:16:58.32,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,This is no duet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.32,0:17:03.07,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,They're seriously duking it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.20,0:17:30.30,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for causing you so much trouble, Pops.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.95,0:17:34.18,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me about it! And when you reach Tokyo,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.18,0:17:36.16,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,first thing you do is get to a barber!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.27,0:17:38.54,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.73,0:17:41.41,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm off.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.27,0:17:45.37,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Brother Jun!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.74,0:17:51.58,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,I'll remember today's session \Nfor the rest of my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.77,0:17:58.23,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Me too, Sen-boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.42,0:18:16.59,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here? I \Ntold you not to see me off.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.59,0:18:19.08,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,I have four questions I want you to answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.47,0:18:22.58,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,If you try to dodge me, I'll \Nget on this train with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.71,0:18:25.33,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,So answer me truthfully.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.83,0:18:30.81,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Question number one: Why did \Nyou tell me not to see you off?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.84,0:18:35.43,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,I hate sad goodbye scenes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.84,0:18:40.23,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Question number two: Didn't \Nyou think to take me with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.15,0:18:44.42,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,The work I'm going to be \Ndoing is kind of a gamble.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.42,0:18:47.30,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I took you with me, there's no \Nguarantee of making any kind of living.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.76,0:18:50.42,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, you're still in high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.42,0:18:51.86,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Question number three...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.87,0:18:56.30,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you do anything \Nmore than kiss me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.74,0:19:01.26,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Did you not touch me because you \Nintended to leave from the start?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.89,0:19:05.75,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.52,0:19:10.75,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,I knew. I knew how much you cared about me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.19,0:19:15.51,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,This is my last question...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.40,0:19:19.85,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Won't you take me with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.30,0:19:25.52,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to take good \Ncare of your own life.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.53,0:19:36.80,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,I figured you would say something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.53,0:19:40.53,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Now it feels like I've been set free, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.07,0:19:44.05,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going back to my own world.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.08,0:19:47.73,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Junichi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.57,0:19:49.54,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.29,0:19:53.67,Main Dialog,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Yurika, where are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.67,0:19:55.55,Main Dialog,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Come out, Yurika!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.85,0:19:58.09,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you embarrass us by walking out
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.09,0:20:00.04,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,in the middle of an arranged \Nmarriage meeting like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.04,0:20:01.55,Main Dialog,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down, dear!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.55,0:20:04.06,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,We're going back there together, Yurika!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.56,0:20:09.06,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Yurika, where are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.95,0:20:19.27,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going back to my own world.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.26,0:20:42.77,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,I dragged you on board...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.27,0:20:45.50,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,Now what?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.77,0:20:50.53,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,What is there to do? The train's \Nalready left the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.53,0:20:51.77,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.56,0:20:56.39,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,Well, when we get there, \Nwe'll go to my room first
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.77,0:20:59.78,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,and maybe I'll have you cut my hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.67,0:21:09.61,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,It's freezing today.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.61,0:21:12.45,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Think I'll light the heater.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.84,0:21:28.64,Songs,,0000,0000,0000,,I waited for you on that slope　
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.56,0:21:36.92,Songs,,0000,0000,0000,,For our after school promise　
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.92,0:21:41.91,Songs,,0000,0000,0000,,There was a 'goodbye' blurred far away　
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.87,0:21:56.22,Songs,,0000,0000,0000,,I was so weak, so awkward, and so fragile back then
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.22,0:22:03.77,Songs,,0000,0000,0000,,But you gave me a small pair of wings　         　　
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.13,0:22:09.83,Songs,,0000,0000,0000,,In the twilight hour of the sky,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.83,0:22:15.48,Songs,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm searching for a gleam of light　　　　　　　
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.48,0:22:23.45,Songs,,0000,0000,0000,,If only I could have said that I love you…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.96,0:22:35.72,Songs,,0000,0000,0000,,The note that I wrote in the corner of my textbook
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.61,0:22:48.80,Songs,,0000,0000,0000,,has never been delivered to this day
